%define sover 0
Name:           zix
Version:        0.4.2
Release:        0
Summary:        A lightweight C library of portability wrappers and data structures
License:        ISC
Group:          Development/Libraries/C and C++
URL:            https://github.com/drobilla/zix
Source0:        https://github.com/drobilla/zix/archive/refs/tags/v%{version}.tar.gz#/%{name}-%{version}.tar.xz
BuildRequires:  cmake
BuildRequires:  doxygen
BuildRequires:  gcc-c++
BuildRequires:  graphviz
BuildRequires:  meson
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig
BuildRequires:  pkgconfig(glib-2.0)

%description
Zix is a lightweight C library of portability wrappers and data structures, such as:
Allocation
Algorithms
Data Structures
Threading
File System

%package        -n libzix-0-%{sover}
Summary:        A lightweight C library of portability wrappers and data structures
Group:          Development/Libraries/C and C++

%description    -n libzix-0-%{sover}
Zix is a lightweight C library of portability wrappers and data structures, such as:
Allocation
Algorithms
Data Structures
Threading
